summary: An Ordinance refunding to J. M. Lanway, of No. 4415 Latona Avenue, Seattle, the sum of Fifteen and 22/100 ($15.22) Dollars, which amount represents and excess taken from him in error in payment of assessment against an undivided one-half of Lot 14, Block 9, Harrison Heights Addition, for the improvement of Bagley Avenue, et al, authorized by Ordinance No. 17684, creating Local Improvement District No. 1670, as evidence by Treasurer's receipt No. X-5498
